<plot>To be on the road without a map, As time flows back to the past. To bleed without a cause... to run without a heart. As fate rains without a warning. To fade without dying... to speak without echoes. As fathers become sons and sons become fathers. To sing without light... to sleep without dreams. To live... To be Homeless.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?244200</url></doc>
